00:09:36.242 --> 00:09:37.777
Samo... Gdje ti je djevojka?

00:09:37.952 --> 00:09:39.379
Djevojka ima ime, tata.

00:09:39.412 --> 00:09:41.956
Ok, gdje je, uh, Jennifer, Michelle...

00:09:41.956 --> 00:09:43.208
Zoe...
- Anna.

00:09:43.208 --> 00:09:44.250
Anna.

