01:12:18.150 --> 01:12:19.852
Mislim da ne moramo ovo pretvoriti u...

01:12:19.852 --> 01:12:22.547
Nevjerojatno da sam mislio...
- Ne, ne, ne...

01:12:22.547 --> 01:12:24.257
